    <stitle>CAB: 7000 AND 8000 SERIES MODELS - LUBRICATION - AS REQUIRED</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>AS REQUIRED</title>
        <para>Lubricate seat adjuster slides with Fleetrite EP Moly grease or equivalent to NLGl No. 2 Multi-Purpose
            Lithium grease.
        </para>
        <para>Lubricate window regulator gear teeth, window regulator lever at cab door window slide block, and cab door
            window slide rail with Lubriplate 105 grease or equivalent.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
